Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.90,0:00:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,《纸牌屋》前情提要...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on House of Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.68,0:00:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,关键问题在于  白宫是否也在某种程度上卷入其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The issue at stake is whether the White House was in any way involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,单是为来自中国的政治献金洗白就是违法的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just the act of laundering Chinese contributions is illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.30,0:00:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,道格拉斯·斯坦普  你的幕僚长\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Douglas Stamper, your chief of staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.97,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是7月14日他在拉尼根的赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is him at Lanagin's casino July 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.80,0:00:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们有证据证明道格出现在不该出现的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have evidence of Doug being where he shouldn't have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是能招致弹劾的罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're talking about impeachable offenses...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-完全不会 先生    -你的幕僚长...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Not at all, sir...    - Your chief of staff was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.31,0:00:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你害怕了  我看得出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're scared. I can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.48,0:00:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我说什么  我就说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll say whatever you want me to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.81,0:00:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,她可能会起诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She could indict you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.90,0:00:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,幕僚就是做这个的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what having a staff is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.19,0:00:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,强如阿喀琉斯  也终被踵上一箭毙命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even Achilles was only as strong as his heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他们声音很响  但我们要发出更高的声音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're loud,but I think we need to be louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,如果法案真能进入辩论 我不会单单退出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the bill goes to the floor as is,I won't just bow out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.03,0:00:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我会积极反对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll actively fight it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,要我说  她也背叛了自己的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you ask me,she's betraying her country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,多线作战  雷米 必须得是杰姬·夏普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Multiple fronts, Remy. Has to be Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,-那我就是对的    -关于什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Then I was right.   - About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你根本不在乎我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How little I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.76,0:00:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她已经会见了一半的国会议员  这女人是要见血\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's interviewed half of Congress.That woman's after blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.55,0:00:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他是在担心他的婚姻咨询 他也该担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's worried about his marriage counseling, as he should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是在担心你的婚姻咨询 你不必担心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're worried about your marriage counseling, you shouldn't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.72,0:00:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你得想想这件事的后果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imagine the fallout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,有个地址老是出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This one address keeps popping up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.35,0:01:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-安德伍德吗    -是总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Underwood?    - The President.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你讲的是法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're parsing the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我讲的则是精神层面的法则\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm talking about a spiritual code.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,保密协议是一份契约\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Confidentiality is a covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.55,0:01:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅在我和接受我咨询的人之间成立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not only between myself and those I counsel,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.87,0:01:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在我自己和上帝之间也成立\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but also between myself and the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,拉金博士  我现在重点关注的是洗钱案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Larkin, my chief focus here is the money laundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.52,0:01:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果总统先生提到过冯山德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the President brought up Xander Feng,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德·塔斯克  还有阿道希赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk, the Adohi Casino--
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不管重点是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It doesn't matter what the focus is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我都不能向你透露私人谈话的内容\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't share anything we discussed privately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.21,0:01:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,宗教指导受法律保护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Religious guidance is protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,但你也提供专业的心理咨询\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you were also conducting professional therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.47,0:01:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这我从未承认过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I never claimed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,基斯先生及太太已经证实了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. And Mrs. Keith confirmed as much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.37,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是去了他们家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were at their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们并没有参与谈话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But they didn't participate in any of our conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,他们又怎么可能知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So how would they know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.19,0:01:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你只提供宗教咨询吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're saying you only gave religious counsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我对我工作的理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's how I choose to interpret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,总统夫妇从没去过你的教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President and his wife have never once attended your church.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至都和你不是一个教派的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not even the same denomination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.83,0:01:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,无关紧要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.64,0:01:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,法律上可紧要得很\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not legally speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对能说服法官发传票给你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm certain I can convince a judge to issue a subpoena
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你并非总统夫妇正式的宗教导师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}on the grounds that you weren't their legitimate spiritual advisor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你的特权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is your prerogative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但我会上诉  我肯定会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I can appeal. And I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定败诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,除非对方放弃保密权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only circumstance by which I would talk
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝不会回答你的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is if someone personally waived their privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.77,0:02:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我宁可被判蔑视法庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Otherwise I'd rather face contempt of court.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这事关道德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a matter of ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,总统先生  你又把沙袋挪回来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. President. Ah, you brought it back in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.06,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,弗洛伊德·梅威瑟{\fs14}[著名拳击手]{\fs20}今早来白宫参观\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Floyd Mayweather visited the White House this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得他看见这个肯定很兴奋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought he'd get a kick out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他没打几拳\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did he have a go at it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.78,0:02:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,他打了套组合拳  我都担心把沙袋打爆了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He threw a combination I thought would bust the stitching loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.64,0:02:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那场面一定很好看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, that must have been a treat to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.80,0:02:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我  这不仅仅是力量的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was telling me it's not just about the power.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,比他更有力量的拳手不少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Plenty of boxers are more powerful than he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,关键是他的战术  他的准头和速度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, it's his tactics, his precision, his speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的一点  就是他的反击\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Most important? His counter punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他躲闪腾挪  选择最完美的时机一拳制胜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He dances and dodges and then picks the perfect moment to strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.11,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听着耳熟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does that sound familiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you mean, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你送我这个沙袋  作为友谊的表示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You gave this to me as a gesture of friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但我现在看着它  却感受不到友谊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I look at this now, I don't see friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.53,0:03:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到的是算计\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你算计我  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You set me up, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你的私下接触  还有特别检察官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your back channeling. The special prosecutor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,再想想雷蒙德  琳达  还有吉姆·马修斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I think about Raymond, about Linda, about Jim Matthews...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你想错了  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are wrong, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.79,0:03:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这是邓巴就婚姻咨询问的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Questions from Dunbar about the marriage counseling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"那是大海里的一根针  还不是邓巴要找的那根"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"It's a needle in the haystack she's not trying to find."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.23,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这是你的原话  她还真就捞着了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's what you said. Well, she found the needle.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.23,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我非常震惊  我绝没\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am shocked, sir. I -- I never --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你震惊才怪  你想削弱我的权威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like hell you are. You want to deminish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.36,0:03:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,削弱你的权威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Diminish you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,为你2016年挑战我打基础\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Laying the groundwork for a challenge in 2016.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.73,0:04:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我无礼  但你这论调太荒唐了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am sorry to have to say this, sir, but you are being ludicrous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你真以为我瞎了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you really think I'm so blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.95,0:04:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,从没有哪个副总统挑战过在位总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A vice president has never challenged a sitting president.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你往上爬的过程中已经做过不少别人不会做的事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've climbed the ladder doing things other men would never do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是为了服务于你和本党的利益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Always in service to you and the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,交出行程记录是你的主意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was you idea to hand over those logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让白宫和中国扯上了关系  还有赌场\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You connected the White House to China, the casino --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是雷蒙德·塔斯克让我们与中国和赌场扯上了关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk entangled us with China and the casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是我及时干预\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if I hadn't intervened --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有弗洛伊德那套腾挪的本事  我识破你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't dodge and duck like Floyd. I've learned your moves now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当了总统就易多疑  你别这样  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This office breeds paranoia. Don't give into it, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.07,0:04:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是会引人非议  我就会要求你辞职了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd ask for your resignation if it wouldn't make things worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但从此刻开始  我不想听你的任何建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But from this moment forward, I don't want to hear your voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,也不想看见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to see your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,再让我看见你  我就让你吃不了兜着走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if I do, I will put you on your god damn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我被驱逐了  我成功将总统和其他人隔开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Exile. I've managed to isolate the president from everyone.
