Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,她对法案的反对是可耻的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her opposition to the bill is disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这会使数以千计的男性和女性\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will cost thousands of men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.78,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,得不到他们应得的公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14} the justice they deserve,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,甚至会毁掉一些人的生活"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and some of them their lives."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.17,0:07:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是梅根·汉纳希的话  他们有失公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those are Megan Hennessey's words. They're biased.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这是克莱尔教她说的  汉纳希不过是传声筒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're Claire's words. Hennessey's just the mouthpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么文中还说我拒绝置评\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why does it say here that I declined to comment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你说过  会惹麻烦的事能躲就躲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you didn't want to kick up dust if we could avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这是《纽约时代杂志》  你应该告诉我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's the New York fucking Times. You should've let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,是我的决定  我承担责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That was my call. I'll take the blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,查明汉纳希接下来会在哪里出现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Find out when Hennessey's next appearance is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我要搞垮这个婊子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna beat this bitch down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道她针对你  但是针对她的话...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know she went after you, but going after her is --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.85,0:07:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不是她  是克莱尔·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not her. Claire Underwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.52,0:07:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道加勒特可能会产生误解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand how Garrett might misconstrue things,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟现在他压力很大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}given the pressure he's under.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.41,0:07:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但你肯定不会相信吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you can't honestly believe it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不知道该相信什么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what to believe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.30,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯非常沮丧  他只是想帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis is devastated. All he wants to do is help,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但他觉得自己受到了冤枉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but he feels like he's being unfairly accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不想相信  克莱尔  但加勒特确信不疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to believe it, Claire, but Garrett is convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.72,0:07:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你能跟他谈谈吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在得集中精力维护我的家庭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have to concentrate on keeping my family together right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是跟他争吵关于...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not getting into arguments over --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,如果弗兰西斯真有什么图谋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If Francis were really up to something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那他怎么不直接把咨询的事告诉邓巴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}don't you think he would have told Dunbar about the therapy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.19,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,他逼我们交出记录就等于那么做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He basically did by forcing us to hand over the logs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是你丈夫的决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your husband chose to hand them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.86,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他拒绝  弗兰西斯是不会逼他的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he'd said no, Francis wouldn't have pressed the issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想跟你争这个  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to debate this with you, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我只求你好好想想这件事  特莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I'm asking is that you really think this through, Tricia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在跟你在一起吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is he with you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不  只有我和你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. It's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我要挂电话了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to get off the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你跟加勒特谈谈好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you please talk to Garrett?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,再见  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Goodbye, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.62,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.58,0:08:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得她会抛开丈夫站在我这边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think she's going to side with me instead of her husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,除了跟你  特莉莎还跟别人说过{\u1}阿普唑仑{\u0}的事吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Tricia tell anyone else about the Xanax besides you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}镇静抗焦虑药
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,应该没有  她对此非常敏感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I doubt she would. She's very sensitive about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她要是跟别人说过  我们就可以把消息传出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she'd only told someone else, then we could just leak it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.93,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这太明显了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But it'll be too obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,医生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他在保护他们  他什么都不会说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's protecting them. He won't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他们放弃保密特权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless they waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那对他们可没有好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They have absolutely nothing to gain by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是对我们有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.12,0:09:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你得去见塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to meet with Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我背叛了他  他为什么还要见我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would he talk to me after I back-stabbed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,正因为如此他才会见你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's precisely why he'll talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能去圣路易斯  你知道的...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I can't go to St. Louis. You know --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.09,0:09:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克会来东部  你要做的就是找到他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tusk will come east. Your job is to get in the same room with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-什么计划    -雷米·丹顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- What's the play?   - Remy Danton.
