Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我来安排\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll set it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.01,0:09:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,道格  一定确保其他方面我们万无一失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Doug? Let's make sure we're airtight on everything else.
