Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"灾难来临了"  用混乱对抗混乱的人说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Cry, 'Havoc,'" Said he who fought chaos with chaos,
