Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,给格林打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put Green on the fucking line, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.83,0:09:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你想说什么  都可以跟我说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything you have to say, you can discuss it with me.
