Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这是美国电话电报公司八个数据中心的访问网格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is the access grid to all eight of AT&T's data centers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你还是解开手铐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what do you say you un-cuff me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后告诉格林特工我在等他的电话吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and tell Agent Green I'll be waiting for his call?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.12,0:10:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我正在试图修复与中国的关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to repair relations with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.33,0:10:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,给冯政治庇护就是一记耳光\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Giving Feng asylum would be a slap in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特有麻烦  他得表现出决心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett's in trouble. He needs to appear resolute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.41,0:10:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的总统有多强  我们就有多强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're only as strong as the president we serve.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须拯救他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have to rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能确定他的证词不会扯上白宫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can you be sure his testimony won't implicate the White House?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.14,0:10:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,他知道谁有奶  谁是娘\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows where his bread is buttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.08,0:10:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你这不是要拯救总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This isn't about you saving the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-当然是    -这不是第一次了  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Of course it is.   - We've been down this road before, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,迈克尔·科恩  亚当·嘉乐威\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Michael Kern, Adam Galloway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我想当国务卿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to become secretary of state
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是为了进行有成效的外交\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in order to engage in productive diplomacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.32,0:10:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,而不是全职损失控制\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not full-time damage control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们要让加勒特回到正轨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why we have to put Garrett back on his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想让他脱轨吧  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want him on his ass, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:10:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是总统这么跟你说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is this what the president told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他现在太多疑了  凯茜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's paranoid, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让大家跟我反目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's trying to turn people against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.11,0:11:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是你自己的行为让大家跟你反目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're turning them against yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你在要求我坑害总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're asking me to undermine the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,假如总统对我的指责属实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's say that what the President has accused me of is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.15,0:11:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这就真的很糟吗  考虑一下这么做的结果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would that be so bad? If taken to its conclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,对你没有好处吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't you stand to benefit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,对国家没有好处吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't the country?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想牵扯进去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want anything to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,就再做一次  凯茜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just one more time, Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,别去管那些条条框框\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's unshackle ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,机会只有一次  冯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a one-time offer, Mr. Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我要白纸黑字写下来  不加任何条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would need it in writing. Open-ended, no restrictions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,法定豁免权也是一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same goes for legal immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.81,0:11:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我要确认\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First I need to know whether or not
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.04,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否通过拉尼根的赌场洗钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you funneled money through Lanagin's casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不  等我安全抵达美国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, no. I will speak freely once I've arrived safely
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.06,0:12:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我才会全盘托出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the United States.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,除非你现在就能提供确凿证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless you provide valuable evidence now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,司法部长不会答应任何豁免权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the attorney general will not grant immunity on any level.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我在中国已经全部否认了这些指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've denied these allegations in China.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我的敌人想置我于死地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My enemies want me dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是逼我给他们证据\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're asking me to give them confirmation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,作为回报  我们会给你提供避难所\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we're giving you safe haven in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我在迪拜已经有避难所了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I already have safe haven in Dubai.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那里的庇护所只是暂时的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your asylum there is only temporary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们给你提供的是永久身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're offering you permanent status.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信他们也会给我永久身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm confident that they will grant me permanent status.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是外交部长亲口跟你说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hear that directly from the Minister of Foreign Affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我刚跟他谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I just spoke to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你连护照都没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Right now you are a man without a passport.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,北京方面还没查封的资产\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever assets Beijing hasn't seized are frozen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.56,0:12:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,也都被所有和中美关系紧密的国家冻结了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in every country with close ties to the United Sates or China,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上是全世界所有国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is just about every country in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.37,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要自由和金钱  我们想要信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want your freedom and fortune. We want information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.91,0:12:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,冯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you need to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.45,0:13:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,向我证实确实有洗钱行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Confirm for me the existence of a money-laundering scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们用赌场来掩饰外资流入\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes. We used the casino to mask foreign contributions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.41,0:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你们中谁跟我讲讲这是怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One of you want to tell me what this is all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.47,0:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你必须得遵从\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to comply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.65,0:13:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说我得出席\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean I have to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.97,0:13:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,除非我们上诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless we appeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会输\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'd lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.71,0:13:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,她要不是证据确凿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She wouldn't have issued the subpoena
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.11,0:13:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,也不会传唤我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}unless she had something substantial.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我同意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是为什么我觉得你该去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is why I think you should go
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,并拒不解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and plead the Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她手上有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you think she has?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想妄加推断\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to speculate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,老天  我付给你们六个一天的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}God damn it, I pay the six of you more in one day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.94,0:13:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,比供个孩子上大学都多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}than it costs to put a kid through college.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我请你们是要你们比我知道得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I pay you to know more than I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她问询时说的对我们会很有帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Her line of questioning will tell us a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.98,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,万一她真要提出指控  我们可以据此准备辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can use that to prepare our defense in case there's an indictment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么时候走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When do I have to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.90,0:13:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的会面是在后天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your interview is the day after next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.80,0:13:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,48小时\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}48 hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.01,0:14:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,发动不了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Having trouble starting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  可能电池没电了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. I think the battery might be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你想试试跨接启动  我有电线\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have some cables if you want to try and jump it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这真的不麻烦吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sure you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.32,0:14:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,一点也不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你真是太好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. It's really nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.64,0:14:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,开引擎盖  我把我车开过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Pop your hood. I'll bring my car around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.18,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.36,0:14:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,这位是彼得  他开车送我回来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is Peter. He's the guy who drove me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这些要放哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where do you want these?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我来拿  谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll take 'em. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:14:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rachel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,丽萨说你俩是室友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa said you two were roommates.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,要我给你拿点什么  来杯水吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can I get you something? A glass of water?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.02,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不用  谢谢  我得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, thanks. I should really get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  太谢谢你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气  希望车能修好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My pleasure. Good luck with the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,希望只是电池没电  晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope it's only a dead battery. Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们应该给他些钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We should give him some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.41,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,彼得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Peter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她得离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She needs to be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟我说她可以留下的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Y-- you told me she could stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我改主意了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你不在乎她在不在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you said you didn't care if she was here --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.40,0:15:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我不需要解释什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't need to explain myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你受不了了  是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't stand it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了我爱上了别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The idea that I might actually love somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了我生命中除了你还有别人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That I might have somebody in my life who isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你在乎她  就让她走  瑞秋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you care about her, make it happen, Rachel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.64,0:15:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,没事  告诉你朋友我不会要钱的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You need to tell your friend that I won't take any money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was happy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都需要好心人帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We all need a good Samaritan every now and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,麦金尼斯将军被判处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you feel justice was served
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,四十年有期徒刑时  你觉得正义得到伸张了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when General McGinnis got sentenced to 40 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}梅根·汉纳希  反性侵活动分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,就他的罪行而言  正义是得以伸张了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, as far as his crimes go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有成千的服役士兵没有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But not for thousands of servicemen and --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉打断你的讲话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm -- I'm sor-- I'm sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我的制作人告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}m-- my producer is telling me that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,杰奎琳·夏普刚打电话来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jacqueline Sharp has called in,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,众议院多数党党鞭  议员女士  您在吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the house majority whip. C-- congresswoman, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我在  克里斯  谢谢你接我的电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I'm here, Chris. And thank you for taking my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,议员女士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Congresswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,首先  作为一名老兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First of all, as a veteran like yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我想感谢你对国家的贡献\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to thank you for your service to our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这是责任  无需感谢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Duty doesn't require thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.22,0:16:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴你提到责任这个话题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm glad you brought up duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.90,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你最近将它称之为洗脑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you recently equated it with brainwashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我的本意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你说"紧跟党派路线"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said "Toeing the party line."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}电话连线  杰奎琳·夏普议员  众议院多数党党鞭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.92,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的本意是文化和体系是...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I meant was that the culture and the system is one that --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是打电话来和你辩论的  梅根\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't call to argue with you, Megan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,恰恰相反\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.03,0:16:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要解决这个问题  就必须找到共同点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't fix this problem until we find some common ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你不觉得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.53,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就我来看这个问题没有妥协空间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no middle ground as far as I'm concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.57,0:16:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,军队需要改变\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The military needs to change --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我都曾经在军中服役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can't we agree that you and I served
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,以保护人民自由辩论的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so that we could protect open debate,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,而这正是民主的基础  你说不是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which is the very bedrock of democracy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,理论上是的  但这不是我要说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, in theory, but that's not what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:17:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是理论上  是实际上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not in theory. In reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的人为了这份自由不惜牺牲生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Brave men and women die fighting for that freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,勇敢的涵义就是为那些和你意见相左的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The meaning of bravery is fighting for the freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也同样享有自由而战斗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of those with whom you disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,当然  但我们回到真正的话题上来好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sure, but let's get back to the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为不勇敢的人是克莱尔·安德伍德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I don't think is brave is Claire Underwood
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,逃避这场辩论  找你替她进行这场斗争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}dodging this debate and having you fight this battle for her instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.19,0:17:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那我为什么在和你而不是她谈话  这是她的法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why am I talking to you instead of her? It's her bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不只是她  是我们共同的成果\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not just hers. It's all of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你勇敢地说出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except one of you is brave enough to say it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.80,0:17:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,而她却是个懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the other is a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.97,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,安德伍德夫人勇敢地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mrs. Underwood was brave enough
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在全国性电视节目上承认她...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to go on national television and admit that she --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  但那之后她去哪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and where has she been since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,应付丑闻  躲避媒体\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Deflecting scandal and hiding from the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.43,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根  你在《纽约时代杂志》上说我可耻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You called me disgraceful in The New York Times, Megan,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.53,0:17:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你当然有这个权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you have every right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也有权说  安德伍德夫人是可耻的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I also have the right to say that Mrs. Underwood is disgraceful,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没有什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because there is nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.57,0:17:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,比当逃兵更可耻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}more disgraceful than running from a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根  我们根本没有...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Megan? That is -- we're not even...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:17:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.30,0:18:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,去国会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To the Capitol.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冯提到我或总统了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Feng mention either me or the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.64,0:18:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴不肯说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dunbar wouldn't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但冯确认了洗钱行为\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the fact that Feng confirmed the money laundering
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,这足以让白宫更受关注\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}increases focus on the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.03,0:18:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,反正我们是清白的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, as long as we're innocent, which we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.37,0:18:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德·塔斯克被传唤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond Tusk has been subpoenaed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么找我们见面  比尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did you ask for this meeting, Bill?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,就为了向我们通报消息吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just keeping us in the loop?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是你让国务卿杜兰特给予冯政治庇护吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you encourage Secretary Durant to offer Feng asylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,比尔  我的天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bill, for god sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,总统也可能问我这个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The president could have asked me that question himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,作为白宫顾问  这是我的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the White House counsel, it is my responsibility --
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, I did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这是杜兰特自己的主意喽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you're saying Durant acted of her own accord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.98,0:18:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道她的动机是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have no idea what her motivations were.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我和总统一样感到震惊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just as shocked as the president
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,她居然没经过他本人允许就擅自而为了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that she would have gone through with this without his direct approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.15,0:18:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,还有一个问题我想和你谈谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's another matter I'd like to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果可以  最好只跟你谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Privately, if we could.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们单独待会儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just give us a few moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-咨询    -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- The therapy.- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.09,0:19:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,具体说  就是放弃保密权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}To be specific, the confidentiality waiver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.64,0:19:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,冯的证词把我们推到一个非常尴尬的位置上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng's testimony puts us in a very awkward position.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.47,0:19:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在面对放弃保密权的极大压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're under a great deal of pressure to waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不放弃  就相当于总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we don't, it implies that the president
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,承认了他没做过的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}may have confessed to things he didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴只是在瞎猜  别让步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dunbar is just grasping. Don't give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.19,0:19:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但拉金宗教指导保密协议的说法并不可靠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But Larkin's argument for spiritual confidentiality is shaky at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想控制事态的发展\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want to control how this thing plays out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.97,0:19:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮什么忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要确保不会再节外生枝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to know if anyone else might pop out of the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.24,0:19:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我没对任何人说过  克莱尔也没说过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I haven't mentioned it to anyone, and neither has Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会辜负总统对我的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would never betray the president's trust like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你抽出时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉总统  我非常难过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tell the president it saddens me that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在只能通过律师交流\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we now have to communicate through lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,要是他想亲自\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will make myself available
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,和我谈谈  我会抽出时间的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if he wants to discuss any of this in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.28,0:19:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.04,0:19:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,梅根的话太过分了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What Megan said was offensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,她不该质疑你的品行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She shouldn't have questioned your character.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.07,0:20:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那都是精心准备的谈话要点  而且不是她准备的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Those were talking points. Carefully crafted, and not by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是来挑衅的  杰姬  我是来解决问题的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not here to pick a fight, Jackie. I'm here to end one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.25,0:20:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,只要法案进行投票  这事就会结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it'll end soon enough when the bill goes to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.88,0:20:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不会进行投票的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It won't go to the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.77,0:20:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我跟艾琳·布鲁克斯谈过了  我要撤销法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've spoken to Elaine Brooks and I'm withdrawing the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.07,0:20:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的有一定道理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What you said had some truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.52,0:20:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,之前你提出\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And early on you offered
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.85,0:20:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起找个折中的办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to sit down with me and find a middle ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我那时拒绝了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I decided to draw a line in the sand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.21,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但勇敢的做法应该是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the braver thing would've been for me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.72,0:20:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,收起我的骄傲  跟你好好谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to swallow my pride and sit down with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你还愿谈  我想重新开始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're still open to that, I'd love to start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你和弗兰克在打什么主意吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you and Frank up to something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一项能通过的法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A passable bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,他让南茜监视我  他把我的个人生活搞得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He had Nancy spy on me. He brought my personal life into --
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,弗兰西斯习惯了事事得逞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Francis is used to getting his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,他会不惜一切确保成功\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he'll do anything to make sure he does,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是对我重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}especially if it's something important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  克莱尔  我很怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, Claire. I'm skeptical.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,之前那样对待你  我们深表歉意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're deeply sorry for the way we've treated you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们想重拾失去的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we want to rebuild the trust we've lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得这可能吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you think that's possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉突然这么来了  我打过电话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry to ambush you. I tried calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.59,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能这么对我  克莱尔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't do this to me, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我说得很清楚  我必须尊重加勒特的意愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was very clear that I have to respect Garrett's wishes --
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是那个  是性侵犯法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not that. The sexual assault bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不会进行投票了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not going to a vote.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,议长从日程中删除了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did the speaker remove it from the docket?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.56,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不  是我撤掉了  我刚跟杰姬谈过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I did. I just spoke to Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为她那样说你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is because of what she said about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.79,0:21:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我主要是担心她接下来会不会对付你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My main concern is that she doesn't come after you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.65,0:21:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你和加勒特接受调查期间绝不能发生这种事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not while you and Garrett are going through the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.30,0:21:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想来告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought you should be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.34,0:21:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我知道这项法案对你有多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because I know how much this bill meant to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你为法案投入了那么多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the work you've put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都投入过  但我们要通过杰姬的法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That we've put in. But we'll pass Jackie's version,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,迈出这一小步  循序渐进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}take this baby step, and build on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,法案的事我很失望\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm disappointed about the bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但不得不说  我松了口气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I have to say, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.56,0:21:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How are you holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你听说凯瑟琳做了什么吗  许诺冯政治避难\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hear what Catherine did? Giving Feng asylum?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:21:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不可原谅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Inexcusable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,加勒特气疯了  他觉得走投无路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Garrett's beside himself. He feels cornered,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.26,0:22:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这下我们除了放弃保密权别无选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like we have no choice but to waive the privileges now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,药物的事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But what about the medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可不是啊  我不该说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. I shouldn't be sharing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不说了  你该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We don't have to talk about it. You should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.15,0:22:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你日程排得很满\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you have a packed schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.55,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.02,0:22:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在走廊里单独找上了她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I had to do was get her alone in a hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.57,0:22:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说杰姬那边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I meant with Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要分清轻重缓急\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have our priorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.79,0:22:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道做这样的放弃并不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know it isn't easy to let go of something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.87,0:22:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,答应我一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Promise me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.15,0:22:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你说吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.49,0:22:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能一个人住在这房子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't live in this house alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.27,0:22:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我哪也不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.86,0:22:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你是这么说  但这事可能事与愿违\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You say that, but this could all backfire.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.30,0:22:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德肯定会拒不解释\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond will plead the Fifth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他提到我  便是承认有罪了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he names me, it's an admission of his own wrongdoing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我更担心加勒特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm more worried about Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你制造了一个有力的对手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You've made a powerful enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.46,0:22:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们比他们强\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're stronger than they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.02,0:22:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可他仍然是总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's still the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证  你被迫做出的一切牺牲之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise you, of all of the sacrifices that you've had to make,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,绝不会包括与一名罪犯离婚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}divorcing a convict will not be one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能放弃保密权  加勒特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't waive the privileges, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.60,0:23:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没别的选择了  冯承认了那笔钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't have a choice anymore. Feng confirmed the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.87,0:23:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,在电话上承认的  不是当面正式承认的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the phone. Not in a formal interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.02,0:23:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,解除对他的庇护  送他回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rescind the asylum. Send him back --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.33,0:23:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,妨碍司法公正\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Obstruction of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.98,0:23:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉利克这么说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Is that what Galich said?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.16,0:23:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,别人肯定会这么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Definitely how it would be perceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们任何不配合调查的举动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And anything we do that looks like a failure to cooperate
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,都会加重他们的猜疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}amplifies that perception.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.33,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是不想公开我们的婚姻问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just don't want our marriage put on display.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴会问我是否提及过中国  我没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, Dunbar'll ask if I brought up China. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拉金能证明我的清白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So Larkin can only help to exonerate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.29,0:23:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,如果婚姻咨询最终进入报告  也无所谓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if the marriage counseling ends up in the report, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能渡过这个难关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can survive that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.68,0:23:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但他给我们开了处方药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he prescribed us medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不算是我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Technically not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.77,0:23:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你在吃我的药  加勒特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You took mine, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.25,0:23:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,拉金知道你会吃才给我开的药\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Larkin wrote the prescription to me knowing you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  你提过了  处方药的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, have you mentioned it? The medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,跟克莱尔吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.09,0:23:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我只能跟她倾诉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. But she's the only person I can talk to
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.53,0:23:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只有她能理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who really understands what it's like --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们更要放弃保密权了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, all the more reason we have to waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他们泄露出去  就由不得我们做主了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they leak this, we can't control the information.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔不会那么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire wouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.03,0:23:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不要小看她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't underestimate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他们要是真准备这么做  现在不早做了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If they were going to, don't you think they would have done it by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她为了减少我们的负担  放弃了性侵法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She dropped the sexual assault bill to reduce pressure on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她也许是这么跟你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That may have been what she told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.23,0:24:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,他们什么都不会说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not going to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.72,0:24:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我求你了  加勒特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm begging you, Garrett.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不要放弃保密权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't waive the privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.99,0:24:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们谈论的事太私密了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The things we talked about were so intimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.06,0:24:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,如果孩子们看到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imagine if the kids --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.14,0:24:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道  但是特莉莎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know. But Tricia --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.29,0:24:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们竞选的时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When we ran,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.24,0:24:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我们的生活将被人仔细审视\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I knew every aspect of our lives would be under scrutiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.12,0:24:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得我们至少还能保护这个\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I thought we could protect at least this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.79,0:24:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,发生在这里的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happens in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.42,0:24:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我会不惜一切保护我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll protect us. Whatever I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.27,0:24:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你要相信我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.04,0:25:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我们检查了USB软件狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We checked the USB dongle.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.17,0:25:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你声称感染了信息中心的代码不在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The code you're claiming infected the data center isn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.14,0:25:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我设计那段代码一到达服务器便自我删除\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I programmed the code to self-erase as soon as it hit the server.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.94,0:25:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在卢卡斯被捕之前就不见了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was gone before Lucas was in cuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.12,0:25:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你信不过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.06,0:25:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是世上最复杂的防火墙之一\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is one of the most sophisticated firewalls in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.45,0:25:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就算真的进去了  也破坏不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Even if your code did get in there, you couldn't break it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.95,0:25:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你妻子手机的运营商就是他们公司\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your wife uses AT&T.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.89,0:25:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,她情人也是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So does her lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.45,0:25:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.51,0:25:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,她现在就在那儿  乔纳森·坎普\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's over there right now. Jonathan Kemp.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.95,0:25:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她的脊椎按摩师  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's her chiropractor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.44,0:25:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想看看他们互发的短信吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want to see their texts to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.58,0:25:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.04,0:25:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看来你早就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, I see you already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.17,0:25:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解你不想把事情闹大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't blame you for not making a fuss,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.56,0:25:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟孩子们还在家里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what with the kids still at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.42,0:25:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但你让我的代码进了那扇门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you walked my code right through that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.64,0:25:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,进入了三千两百万人的手机里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Into 32 million people's phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.65,0:25:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这都怪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And that's on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.51,0:26:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,联调局也罪责难逃  这会闹得很难看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's on the FBI. And it is a shit-storm
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.21,0:26:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让联调局面临国会的调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that will bring the Bureau right in front of Congress.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.17,0:26:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你告诉我  平息这一切要多大代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you tell me: How much is making that disappear worth?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.38,0:26:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你面临一百年的监禁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have a hundred years hanging over your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.75,0:26:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,敲诈联调局对你没好处\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Extorting the FBI won't help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.47,0:26:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是道格拉斯·斯坦普让你陷害卢卡斯·古德温的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did Douglas Stamper tell you to set up Lucas Goodwin?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.50,0:26:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,反恐主管\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Counter-Terrorism Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.65,0:26:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,跟白宫联络官相比真是一步登天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a big step up from White House Liaison.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.54,0:26:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-我认为你背后有推手    -胡说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I think you had a helping hand.   - Not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.46,0:26:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,继续编  但以下是我的要求\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep lying. Meanwhile, here's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,第一  我不再是你的走狗了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, I'm no longer your bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.07,0:26:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,第二  撤销对我的所有指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Two, all of my charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.25,0:26:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,第三  撤销所有对巴利特·布朗的指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three, all of Barrett Brown's charges are dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.44,0:26:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这得看联邦检察官的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's up to the U.S. Attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.66,0:26:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你去想办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.49,0:26:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我听得没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I'm hearing you correctly,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.41,0:26:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你是想要拉金的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you'd like to keep Larkin's testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,侧重在洗钱上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}focused on the money laundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.42,0:26:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,而我从来没提过  因为我毫不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which I never brought up, because I knew nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.29,0:26:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但你担心其他的事  私人的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But your concern is other matters. Private matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.40,0:26:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这些和调查无关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which are irrelevant to the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.08,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能阻止邓巴问问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't prevent Dunbar from asking what she's gonna ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.36,0:26:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,当然不能\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.60,0:26:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我最多只能去拜托拉金博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The most I can do is ask Dr. Larkin
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.20,0:27:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,跟他对下部分问题的回答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}how he would respond to certain questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.42,0:27:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,但他很聪明  会明白我的目的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's a smart man. He'll understand what I'm getting at.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.66,0:27:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这路子合法吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this approach keeps us within the law?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.40,0:27:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没有干扰证词吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're not tampering with testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.64,0:27:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,界线很模糊  但我会确保合法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a fine line. But I'll stay on the right side of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.96,0:27:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他不见我  弗兰克  就像他对你一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He shut me out, Frank. Just like he did with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.85,0:27:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我的副国务卿被委派了全权外交权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My undersecretary has been assigned full diplomatic authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.07,0:27:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时的挫折  凯茜  我到哪你到哪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A temporary setback, Cathy. Where I go, you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.02,0:27:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,现在总统正在战况室\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}At this very moment, the President is in the Situation Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.41,0:27:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,中方对冯的政治庇护的反应跟我预想的一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}China responded to Feng's asylum exactly the way I predicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.30,0:27:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们增派了一倍海军前往与那国岛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're doubling their naval presence off the coast of Yonaguni.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.11,0:27:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你猜谁被赶出战况室了  你和我  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And you know who isn't in the Situation Room? You and I, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.45,0:27:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你只盯着眼下一时的得失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're thinking about where we are
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.02,0:27:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,却对情势的发展方向视而不见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}instead of where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.56,0:27:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这可不像那个在杰斐逊舞会上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now that isn't the Catherine Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.48,0:27:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,和我共舞华尔兹的凯瑟琳·杜兰特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that I waltzed with at the Jefferson Ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.92,0:27:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她深明大势所趋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She understood potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.87,0:27:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,她盯着未来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She had her eyes toward the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.97,0:27:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我对那个凯瑟琳·杜兰特说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told that Catherine Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.64,0:28:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要她这样的人领导国务院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we needed her in the State Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.43,0:28:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也是如此  真不知她哪去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We still need her. I wish I knew where she was,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.36,0:28:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她和我眼前这个凯瑟琳·杜兰特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because she is not the Catherine Durant
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.35,0:28:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是两种人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}sitting in front of me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.35,0:28:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但我跟你说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'll tell you something,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.47,0:28:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她不赶快回来的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If she doesn't show up soon, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.39,0:28:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那这支华尔兹  我只好独自舞下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna have to keep waltzing alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.66,0:28:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because I am done trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.91,0:28:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不想再去说服我面前的这个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}convince this woman in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.92,0:28:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,和我携手前行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to take my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.68,0:28:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你快忙去吧  我不留你了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, don't let me keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.74,0:28:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我就在这儿  我哪也不去  弗兰克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here. I'm not going anywhere, Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.22,0:28:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在能拿到总统简报吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You still have access to the presidential briefing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.33,0:28:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,能  就在我手上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes, I have it right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.23,0:28:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我说说与中国之间的全部情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Walk me through everything that's going on with China.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.83,0:28:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,冯也出场了  也许我们用得上他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng is in play now. We might be able to use him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.75,0:28:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么用\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.52,0:28:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.21,0:28:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然他在北京眼里是有价值的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's clearly valuable to Beijing,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.54,0:29:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那么他对我们就也有价值\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}which makes him valuable to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.01,0:29:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,从没提起过冯山德吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing about Xander Feng?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.16,0:29:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.94,0:29:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,丹尼尔·拉尼根呢  还有雷蒙德·塔斯克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daniel Lanagin? Raymond Tusk?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.00,0:29:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只谈了他的婚姻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We only discussed their marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.58,0:29:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,从未涉及白宫的公务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing about the business of the White House.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.10,0:29:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,他可曾间接提起过与工作有关的压力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any oblique reference to work-related pressures he was feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.40,0:29:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,他说他现在睡眠太少\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said he wasn't getting as much sleep as he'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.25,0:29:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你给他开过什么药物吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you ever prescribe him any medication?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.11,0:29:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,正如我一贯声称  我只提供宗教咨询\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As I've always stated, I provided religious counsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.00,0:29:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白  但我问的是药物处方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I understand. But I'm asking about medication.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.83,0:29:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么关系吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How is this relevant?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.05,0:29:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我想查证他的判断力是否因此受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm trying to assess whether his judgment may have been impaired.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.97,0:29:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在我看来  他和他的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In my opinion, he and his wife
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.19,0:29:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,面对的是典型的婚姻问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were dealing with standard marital issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.41,0:29:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你这是答非所问  拉金博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's not what I asked, Dr. Larkin.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.96,0:29:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我再问第三遍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So I will ask for a third time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.38,0:29:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,而且问得更明确些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And let me be more specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.50,0:29:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,美利坚合众国总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Was any medication prescribed
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.06,0:29:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在接受你的咨询服务时  你是否提供过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or taken as a result of your counseling session
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.63,0:29:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,任何形式的处方或者药物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by the President of the United States?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.86,0:29:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他的工作能力完全没有受影响\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His faculties were operating at a hundred percent,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.26,0:29:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你是想问这个的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if that's what you're asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.50,0:30:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是有政府方面的人和你谈过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Has anyone from the administration spoken to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.01,0:30:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.87,0:30:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,关于取证  是不是有人找过你  指导过你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About this deposition. Has anyone approached you, coached you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.59,0:30:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你现在承认  我会将此认定为及时申报\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you tell me now, I will qualify that as a timely declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.42,0:30:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想继续了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.09,0:30:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,总统放弃了他的保密权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The President waived his privilege.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.63,0:30:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但我是自愿作证的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm here voluntarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.33,0:30:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,拉金博士  一开始你不肯作证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dr. Larkin, at first you wouldn't talk to me
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.64,0:30:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那有违你的道德准则\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because it violated your ethical code.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.31,0:30:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我尊重你的选择\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.36,0:30:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我要问你  作为一个虔诚之人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But let me ask you, as a man of faith
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.50,0:30:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蓄意对我说谎  难道就不违反你的道德准则吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is deliberately lying to me an exception to that code?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.30,0:30:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你拒绝说出实情的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because that is what you're doing
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.91,0:30:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就有作伪证的嫌疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by refusing to share the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.19,0:30:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.82,0:30:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这法案过不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't going to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.69,0:30:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但你说我们就要争取到足够的支持了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you said we almost had the votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.75,0:30:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要能完全确定  但实情并非如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We needed to be a hundred percent solid, and we weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.83,0:30:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,如果法案未能通过  我们的努力就白费了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the bill failed, that would set us back.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.29,0:30:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须接受渐进的改革方案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to accept incremental reform.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.66,0:30:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你的口气跟杰姬·夏普一模一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You sound just like Jackie Sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.38,0:30:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我现在与她合作了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm actually working with her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.69,0:30:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一个有力的盟友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She's a powerful ally for us to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.01,0:30:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可她那样让我下不来台\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After what she did to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.78,0:31:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还公开羞辱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}After what she said about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.86,0:31:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是被他人的非议所左右\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If I let the things people say about me get under my skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.71,0:31:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我连家门都出不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wouldn't be able to leave my own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.14,0:31:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道结果会怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know how this will go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.27,0:31:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都会说"太好了  我们取得了成功"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everyone will say, "Great, we did something,"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.80,0:31:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但其实一无所成\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Which is really nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.50,0:31:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会高兴一时  然后就抛诸脑后忘个干净\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They'll pat themselves on the back and they'll forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.89,0:31:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们让人们注意这个话题了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We helped put this on the radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.09,0:31:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我们是要真正改变现状\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought we were doing something real.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.44,0:31:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,改变人们的生活  幼稚死了  对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Changing people's lives. How naive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.98,0:31:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但至少我不愿意放弃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But at least I didn't want to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.19,0:31:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也许杰姬·夏普说对了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe Jackie Sharp is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.00,0:31:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈就是个懦夫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are a fucking coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.41,0:31:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,是我鼓励你站出来说出你的遭遇\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the one that pulled you out from under the covers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.63,0:31:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,之前你在逃避  靠吃药度日\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were hiding. You and your pills.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,编造各种谎言自欺欺人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So you tell yourself whatever you need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.31,0:31:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我失态了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.79,0:31:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有些政治现实  是我们无法忽视的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There were political realities we couldn't ignore.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.94,0:31:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你想没想过为什么那么多人憎恨华盛顿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you ever wonder why so many people hate Washington?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.19,0:31:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是因为你这种人说那种屁话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's because of people like you using phrases like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.21,0:32:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.50,0:32:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,虽说该开灯  但既然花钱住进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd turn the lights on, but when you're paying for the room
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.31,0:32:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,风景最好的房间  就不如欣赏个够\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}with the best view you might as well make the most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.16,0:32:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没上过顶层  你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've never been in the penthouse here. Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.32,0:32:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么情况\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.51,0:32:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道我为什么来华盛顿吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know why I'm in D.C.?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.54,0:32:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系  雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, it's okay, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.90,0:32:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你能说出的话我都已经知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's nothing you can say that I don't already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.65,0:32:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,冯要去作证了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Feng is on his way to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.52,0:32:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不管赛斯跟你说了什么都不要信他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever Seth has told you, don't believe a word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.59,0:32:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他会说什么我不该相信的事呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What might he have told me that I shouldn't believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.91,0:32:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟副总统见面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You met with the Vice President.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.79,0:32:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,在一座教堂里  别装作没这回事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a church. Don't pretend you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.21,0:32:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,想当墙头草吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Playing both sides?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.51,0:32:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond, look --
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.14,0:32:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我想听你说出来  你跟弗兰克见面了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want to hear you say it. That you met with Frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.17,0:32:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我会跟你说的  雷蒙德  但他不能在这儿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'll talk to you, Raymond, but not with him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.09,0:32:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你先出去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.21,0:32:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,要我在电梯里等你吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Should I hold the elevator for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.44,0:33:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,滚你妈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.12,0:33:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好  那你走楼梯吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. You can take the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.84,0:33:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在耍你  雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're toying with you, Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.31,0:33:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  但是你也一样  雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No doubt. But so are you, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.04,0:33:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我是想哄骗弗兰克  让他以为已经安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I wanted to lead Frank on, give him a false sense of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.65,0:33:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你要说谎  那就说得漂亮点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you're gonna lie, lie better than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.87,0:33:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,他们想离间我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They want to tear us apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.75,0:33:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要多条退路  这我不怪你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't blame you for wanting to keep your options open.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.66,0:33:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但你显然买错了保险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But clearly you have bought the wrong insurance policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.49,0:33:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样搬起石头砸自己的脚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't shoot yourself in the foot like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.60,0:33:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脚  石头也是你拿着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your foot. And you're holding the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.42,0:33:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,去找个别的地方流血吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now go someplace else to bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.57,0:33:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你想谈谈流血吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to talk about blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.88,0:33:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你与弗兰克的这场战争已经让你流了多少血了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much have you spilt in this war with Frank?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.48,0:33:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的一切都是为了维护和平\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All I've tried to do is keep the peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.55,0:33:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你本可让他占上风\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could've let him have the upper hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.04,0:33:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,除了你的自尊  还会让你损失什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What would that have really cost you, other than your pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.65,0:33:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Such a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.27,0:34:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚树立了身家420亿的敌人  雷米\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have just made 42 billion enemies, Remy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.22,0:34:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,外加一些零头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And some change.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.52,0:34:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,390亿  雷蒙德  你的市值在缩水\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}39 billion, Raymond. Your market cap is shrinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.30,0:34:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫顾问比尔·嘉利克今早被特别检查官\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}White House Counsel Bill Galich was called into questioning this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.95,0:34:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}比尔·嘉利克
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.42,0:34:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,希瑟·邓巴传唤质询\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}by Special Prosecutor Heather Dunbar.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.78,0:34:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,从邓巴办公室得到的消息称\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to Dunbar's office,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.46,0:34:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}there are suspicions that
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.12,0:34:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉利克可能干预了证人证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Galich may have tampered with witness testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.99,0:34:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这名证人是托马斯·拉金博士\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The witness in question is Dr. Thomas Larkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.77,0:34:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,一位牧师与咨询师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a reverend and therapist
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.17,0:34:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,据称他为总统和第一夫人进行了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who allegedly conducted secret marriage counseling sessions
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.09,0:34:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,秘密婚姻咨询\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for the president and first lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.36,0:34:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有来自总统的明确指示\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House counsel wouldn't be manipulating testimony
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.96,0:34:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫顾问是不会去干预证词的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}without explicit direction from the Oval Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.20,0:34:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,同样让人不安的是  我们的总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And just as disconcerting is the fact that our president
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.44,0:34:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在寻求心理治疗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is seeking psychological treatment
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.98,0:34:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,并且向美国人民隐瞒这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and chose to hide this from the American people.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.96,0:34:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,如果在这方面我们无法信任他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we can't trust him about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.10,0:34:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们又怎么知道他是否与洗钱阴谋有关呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then how do we know he wasn't involved in a money-laundering scheme?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.19,0:34:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么知道他的精神状况适合来领导我们呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How do we know he's mentally fit to lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.56,0:34:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,最重要的是  如果他知法犯法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And most important, how can he enforce the law
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.73,0:34:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,又如何维护法律\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}when he's breaking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.86,0:34:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为我们众议院的同事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I believe our colleagues in the House certainly have enough
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.81,0:34:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,已经有足够理由考虑弹劾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to consider Articles of Impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.52,0:35:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,信任与法律都被践踏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Both trust and laws have been broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.95,0:35:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不管众议院作何打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whatever the House decides to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.28,0:35:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这位总统必须承担责任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we must hold this president accountable.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.45,0:35:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,全力支持总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fully support the president
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.42,0:35:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不管发生什么都跟他站在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and will stand by him no matter what comes his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.43,0:35:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,揽进来  处理掉  给我找艾拉·萨伊德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Put that in, put it out. Then get me Ayla Sayyad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.44,0:35:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,至于雷米  让他再多倒霉一阵子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And as for Remy, let's let him wither on the vine a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.69,0:35:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,同时  让他的另一半明天来众议院\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the meantime, have his better half come by the house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.53,0:35:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,雷蒙德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Raymond?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.75,0:35:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.37,0:35:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,塔斯克先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Tusk.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.52,0:35:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,邓巴女士  我活了67年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, Ms. Dunbar, in 67 years on this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.61,0:35:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还从来没被传唤过\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have never once been issued a subpoena.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.70,0:35:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,现在总算可以从遗愿清单上划掉了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can now cross that off my bucket list.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.56,0:35:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,此次会面将被记录和封存\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This interview is being recorded and sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.99,0:36:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,如传票所述  塔斯克先生  我与冯山德谈过了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}As the subpoena mentioned, Mr. Tusk, I spoke with Xander Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.51,0:36:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,他指证你与他合作  自2005年以来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He verified that you were his partner
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.26,0:36:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,将中国资金洗白并流入超级政治行动委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in laundering Chinese money to political Super PACs since 2005.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.14,0:36:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你如何回应他的指控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How would you respond to his allegations?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.10,0:36:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客户要行使宪法第五修正案赋予的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My client exercises his right to plead the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.81,0:36:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你是否曾用这些捐赠来换取政治利益\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you ever use these contributions to bargain for political favors?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.34,0:36:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客户要行使宪法第五修正案赋予的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My client exercises his right to plead the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.58,0:36:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你跟丹尼尔·拉尼根是什么关系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What was your relationship with Daniel Lanagin?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.76,0:36:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我的客户要行使宪法第五修正案赋予的权利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My client exercises his right to plead the Fifth Amendment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.73,0:36:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都记不得我为什么要来这儿了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't even remember why I came over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.53,0:36:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说你最初来我家吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean when you first showed up?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.44,0:36:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我是说来厨房\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. To the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.17,0:36:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉  别认为我不爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry. Please don't think that I don't love you --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.82,0:36:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那是为什么  我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then why? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.24,0:37:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一切发展得太快了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything's been so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.26,0:37:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,还有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.87,0:37:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  很难说清  但我还没准备好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know. It's hard to explain, but I'm not ready for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.02,0:37:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,-都是胡说    -不是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- That's bullshit.   - No, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.22,0:37:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在努力适应新生活\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm still trying to figure out this new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.63,0:37:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这一切太让人搞不清\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And this is too confusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.17,0:37:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只有这是清清楚楚的  这你知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is the only thing that's clear, and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你在害怕  但这是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're afraid, but it's good to be afraid when you're--
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.47,0:37:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你得离开  为了你自己好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need you to leave, okay? For your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.21,0:37:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我只会伤害你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am just gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.68,0:37:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我比你想得坚韧得多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have thicker skin than you can even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.29,0:37:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别把事情搞得太痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please don't make this harder than it has to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.46,0:37:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天一切都还好好的  这么突然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everything was fine yesterday. It's so sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.47,0:37:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,简直莫名其妙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's like it's coming out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.75,0:37:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是这样  我已经考虑了一段时间了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, it's not. I've been thinking about it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.98,0:37:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有  否则我会察觉的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you haven't. I would have sensed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.62,0:37:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能请你  拜托你走就是了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you please, please, please just go?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.28,0:37:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我发生了什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.90,0:37:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我不指望你会理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't expect you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.02,0:37:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,也许你可以试着...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, maybe if you try --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.92,0:37:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想让你待在这儿  好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't want you here. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.23,0:37:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我不像你爱我那样爱着你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't love you the way that you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.35,0:37:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,只是利用你  因为有你陪着感觉很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was using you because it felt good to have you around,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.05,0:37:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但那样很自私\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it was selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.63,0:37:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我说那些话  因为我知道你爱听\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said the words because I knew you wanted to hear 'em,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.92,0:37:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不是真心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I didn't mean 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.71,0:37:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想继续说下去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I don't want to keep saying 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.47,0:38:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我出去走一会儿  你收拾东西吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna go for a walk while you pack your stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.16,0:38:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我不要这儿的任何东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I don't want anything that's been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.74,0:38:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,丽萨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lisa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.53,0:38:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,"四面的山洼雾气氤氲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There was a steaming mist in all the hollows,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.20,0:38:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,凄凉地往山顶涌动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it roamed in its forlornness up the hill,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.32,0:38:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}双城记
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.67,0:38:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,仿佛是个邪恶的精灵  寻找歇脚之地而不得\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}like an evil spirit, seeking rest and finding none.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.77,0:38:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那雾粘乎乎的  冰寒彻骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A clammy, and intensely cold mist,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.18,0:38:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,缓缓地在空中波浪式地翻滚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it made it its slow way through the air in ripples
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.34,0:38:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,一浪一浪清晰可见  然后宛如污浊的海涛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that visibly followed and overspread one another,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.95,0:38:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.88,0:38:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,彼此渗诱  融合成了一片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}as the waves of an unwholesome sea might do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.31,0:38:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,雾很浓  车灯几乎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was dense enough to shut out everything
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.64,0:38:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也照不见"\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from the light of the coach lamps."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.91,0:39:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,很惊讶你想和我聊聊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm surprised you wanted to speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.98,0:39:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不是很受政府欢迎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I haven't been the biggest friend of the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.86,0:39:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,难道不是找你谈话的最佳理由吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that the very best reason to speak with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.64,0:39:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我想开始录音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd like to begin recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.97,0:39:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请便\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.11,0:39:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,许多政治分析家预测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A number of political analysts predict
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.97,0:39:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,众议院司法委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the House Judiciary Committee
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.34,0:39:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,将就弹劾条款开始听证会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will commence with hearings on Articles of Impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.75,0:39:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,先就此打住\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's just stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.27,0:39:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你说的这些分析家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So these analysts you speak of,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.10,0:39:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在邓巴的报告发表前就做出预测\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they're making predictions prior to Dunbar's report even being released.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.12,0:39:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,报告出来可能得好几个月\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That could take months.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.17,0:39:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,司法委员会绝不会等那么久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no way the Judiciary will sit on this for that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.60,0:39:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这不正是听证会的根本问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And isn't that the fundamental flaw with these hearings?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.58,0:39:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为包括你在内的媒体记者提出的假设\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The committee feels compelled to act because of hypotheses
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.97,0:39:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,委员会觉得必须采取行动\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}advanced by those in the media, such as yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.94,0:39:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能代表我所有的同行  但我只是报道事实\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't speak for all of my colleagues, but I'm just reporting facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.57,0:39:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能会说这是事实  但实话说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, you may call them facts, but if we're being honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.84,0:39:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,-难道不是    -每篇文章和采访中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- aren't they just --   - In every article and interview,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.01,0:39:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我都只是提出怀疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I report alleged activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.09,0:39:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,怀疑重复的次数够多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you repeat allegations enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.17,0:39:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一遍一遍  反反复复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}again and over and over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.10,0:40:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,那就三人成虎了  这是人之常情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}people start to believe that they're true. That's human nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.44,0:40:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我做过调查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I've done my research.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.60,0:40:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,冯山德已经承认洗钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Xander Feng admitted to the money laundering.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.45,0:40:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但你已经不报道冯山德了  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're no longer writing about Xander Feng. Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.81,0:40:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在报道政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're writing about the administration.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.62,0:40:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,事实上  听证会就是由媒体报道引发的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, these hearings have been initiated by the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.74,0:40:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心的是总统会遭到媒体的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And my fear is that the president will be tried by the press.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.02,0:40:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信他是无罪的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you believe he's innocent?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.06,0:40:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.90,0:40:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我在书面声明中这么写  我现在也还要这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I said so in my written statement and I say so again now.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.19,0:40:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,白宫的法律顾问已经否认了干预拉金博士的证词\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The White House counsel has denied coaching Dr. Larkin,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.49,0:40:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-但根据...    -不管最终发现了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- but according to Ms. --   - Whatever comes to light,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.35,0:40:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,都只会证明总统的清白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it will only prove the president's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.50,0:40:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你为什么  加勒特·沃克是我所认识的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'll tell you why. I have never known anyone more honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.74,0:40:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最诚实  正直  爱国的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}ethical, and patriotic than Garrett Walker.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.25,0:40:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他对我国宪法和法律的尊重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His reverence for the Constitution and the laws of this country
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.85,0:40:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,无人能及\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are surpassed by none.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.77,0:40:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,特莉莎和我有幸拥有一段坚固忠诚的婚姻\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tricia and I have been blessed with a strong and loving marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.55,0:40:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但再坚固的婚姻也会面临挑战\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But even strong marriages face challenges.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.30,0:40:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就像成百万的美国人一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like millions of Americans,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.42,0:40:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们向一位宗教导师寻求建议\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we sought counseling from a spiritual advisor,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.10,0:40:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,而他恰好也是一位职业治疗师\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}one who happened also to be a professional therapist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.08,0:40:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,多年来我们经常\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Over the years we have often
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.60,0:41:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在困境中向我们的信仰寻求帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}turned to our faith in times of adversity.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.69,0:41:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,很多人批评我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Many have criticized us.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.87,0:41:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们宁愿要一位不去寻求帮助的总统吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But would you rather have a president that doesn't ask for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.59,0:41:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我每一天都会请我妻子帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I ask for help from my wife every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.79,0:41:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相扶相依已经有23年了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've relied on one another for 23 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.42,0:41:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起养育了两个漂亮的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've raised two beautiful children together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.68,0:41:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}华尔街电讯报  副总统维护总统
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.62,0:41:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,一起走过了竞选之旅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Endured the campaign trails together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.87,0:41:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,从州首府丹佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the state capital in Denver
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.95,0:41:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,一路来到国家首都\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the nation's capital,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.70,0:41:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直都在彼此身边\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we've always been at each other's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.11,0:41:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我嫁给这个人的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I married this man for the
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.03,0:41:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,和你们很多人选他的原因一样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}same reason that so many of you voted for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.92,0:41:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他是一位信徒  因为他热爱家人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he's a man of God. Because he believes in family.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.19,0:41:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他有同情心和爱心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he is compassionate and loving.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.69,0:41:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,人无完人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, none of us are perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.97,0:41:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是  特莉莎也不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not. Tricia's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.04,0:41:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管她很接近完美了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Although she certainly comes close.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.92,0:41:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好  冯先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good morning, Mr. Feng.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.28,0:41:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我不会否认我作为凡人的极限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I won't ignore what makes me human.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.85,0:41:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,否则只是盲目\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's a form of blindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.83,0:41:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好的领导者应该正视自己的缺点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good leadership means tackling my imperfections head on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.17,0:42:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,对一个在逃亡的人来说不错嘛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not bad for a man on the run.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.50,0:42:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你是说对一个有豁免权的人来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You mean a man with immunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.76,0:42:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,随便你想怎么说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wherever you're most comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.50,0:42:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有很多事要谈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a lot to discuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.07,0:42:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我是在了解情况的前提下这么做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I do so with open eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的爱也是明明白白的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just as I love, with open eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.68,0:42:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,爱我的妻子  爱上帝\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my wife, my maker,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.27,0:42:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,爱我的国家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and my country.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.11,0:42:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,请进\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.36,0:42:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  密查姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thank you, Meechum.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.70,0:42:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬  一般来说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie, in these circumstances
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.81,0:42:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我会去找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}normally I would come to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.46,0:42:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但现在我们还是保持距离为好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but we need to keep a public distance for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为我是来讨论性侵法案的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought I was here to discuss the sexual assault bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.95,0:42:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  还有其他的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are. Among other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.85,0:42:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.06,0:42:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你有条件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's a price.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.55,0:42:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要这样说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we don't think of it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.51,0:42:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不管今天你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going to support your bill,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.84,0:42:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我都会支持你的法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter what you say today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.99,0:42:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Regarding?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.23,0:42:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,弹劾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impeachment.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.53,0:43:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,如果事情真闹到司法委员会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, if it goes to the Judiciary --
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.31,0:43:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎肯定是会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It most definitely will.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.44,0:43:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我不那么肯定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not sure about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.94,0:43:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看了总统的声明了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you see the president's address?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.44,0:43:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们看了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.24,0:43:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得能起些作用  控制事态\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think it will help. Stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.22,0:43:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,而且弹劾可以被否决\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Impeachment can be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.86,0:43:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,但那是我们要避免的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But that's we need to avoid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.42,0:43:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望弹劾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want impeachment...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.08,0:43:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要打一场明知会输的仗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why fight a losing battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.07,0:43:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在众议院是多数党\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a majority in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.03,0:43:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,现在是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.06,0:43:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果本党不能和一个污点总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But if this party fails to distance itself
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.77,0:43:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,划清界限\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}from a toxic president...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.88,0:43:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在做长远打算\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're thinking ahead here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.64,0:43:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才会找你就法案的事和解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's why I came to you about the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.12,0:43:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不值得为它翻脸\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because it wasn't worth burning a bridge over.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.31,0:43:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,长远来讲  我们合作的好处更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In the long run we have a lot more to gain by working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.86,0:43:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.90,0:43:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你在《电讯报》采访的时候说你会\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said in the Telegraph article that you would sta--
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.66,0:43:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须那么说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.96,0:43:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我的办公室跟总统的只隔了三间屋子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My office is three doors down from the president's.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.34,0:43:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能公开诋毁他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't publicly deride him.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.34,0:43:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你希望我来做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want me to do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.83,0:43:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我们希望你做你最拿手的  拉选票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We want you to do what you do so well: whip the votes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.60,0:44:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能背叛总统\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't abandon the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.39,0:44:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个党救了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If the party rescues him,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.39,0:44:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我们将在中期选举时失去50个席位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we'll lose 50 seats in the House in the midterms.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.39,0:44:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你会失去你在领导层的地位\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You will lose your position in the leadership.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.07,0:44:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要花十年\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it will take us a decade
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.54,0:44:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,重新赢得选民的信任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to regain the trust of the electorate.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.37,0:44:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只求你肯听取意见\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All we're asking is that you have an open mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.25,0:44:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,克莱尔就是如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Claire kept an open mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.65,0:44:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你得以修改性侵法案\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and you'll pass sexual assault reform as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.08,0:44:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能把弹劾和...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't possibly compare impeachment to --
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.31,0:44:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,只是举个例子  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's an illustration, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.22,0:44:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,说明未来会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of what the future looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.11,0:44:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们提出的  是进步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What we offer is progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.83,0:44:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,并保证日后还会有更多进步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With a promise of more to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.98,0:44:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是个开始  杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's only the beginning, Jackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.23,0:44:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,坚决  务实  记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ruthless pragmatism, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.12,0:44:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我才选你做党鞭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's why I wanted you to be the whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.96,0:44:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们三个是同一类人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The three of us, we're cut from the same cloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.25,0:45:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,副总统先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Vice President,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.37,0:45:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你要我做的  几乎是叛国\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}what you're asking is just shy of treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.13,0:45:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,几乎  也就是政治\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just shy. Which is politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.41,0:45:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小心  那很易碎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Be careful. It's delicate.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.32,0:45:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.30,0:45:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,一件我做了很久的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something I've been working on for a very long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.04,0:45:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要完成了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it's nearly finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.14,0:45:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,杰姬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jackie?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.17,0:45:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我们完成吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Help us finish it.
